content: That's not mobile at all. First of all, there is no infinite scroll for you reports. Meaning that if you have many visuals on the same page, you won't be able to integrate all of them on the mobile view canvas. Buttons does not work very well. Tables are not really responsive (you cannot set an auto-columns width just for the mobile view). On top of that, this mobile view is just avalaible for the mobile app, not for the published-to-web reports or online reports. A shame in 2020.
